short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Melvor 1.2 Autoeater helps your character to survive by eating food when your health is low.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Note: This is for web version and keep the tab active for this to work.

Note: Make sure to have enough food.

In every 2 seconds this checks if the HP is 40% or lower then performs a rapid eating until having 90% of HP back. Make sure to have enough food.
